name: NAPD 1
notes: Chron uses 2 radiocarbon dates on hearths plus 2 averaged dates. The date 12134±31 (uppermost dung layer) is an average of 22 dung samples. The date of 14857±182 (lowermost dung layer) is an average of 7 wood samples.
